bid.name: bid
bid.description: Highest price a buyer will currently pay for a security

bid_eod.name: bid_eod
bid_eod.description: Previous Closing Bid. Highest price the buyer will pay for an option at the time of previous market close

ask.name: ask
ask.description: Lowest price at which a seller will currently sell a security

ask_eod.name: ask_eod
ask_eod.description: Previous Closing Ask. Lowest price at which the seller will sell an option at the time of previous market close

close_eod.name: close_eod
close_eod.description: Previous closing price. The price at close of the most recent trading day

last.name: last
last.description: Last Price. Current price for stocks and implied price for indexes

change.name: change
change.description: Change between the current and previous night's stock price

changepercent.name: changepercent
changepercent.description: Percent change between the current and previous night's stock price

changeopen.name: changeopen
changeopen.description: Change between the current and opening stock price

changepercentopen.name: changepercentopen
changepercentopen.description: Percentage change between the current and opening stock price

change_eod.name: change_eod
change_eod.description: Previous Day Change. Change between the day before last's closing option bid/ask mid-price and previous day's closing value

changepercent_eod.name: changepercent_eod
changepercent_eod.description: Percentage change between the day before last's closing option bid/ask mid-price and previous day's closing value

highprice52wk_eod.name: highprice52wk_eod
highprice52wk_eod.description: 52 Week High. Highest closing stock price during previous 52 weeks

lowprice52wk_eod.name: lowprice52wk_eod
lowprice52wk_eod.description: 52 Week Low. Lowest closing stock price during previous 52 weeks

dividenddate_eod.name: dividenddate_eod
dividenddate_eod.description: Dividend Date. Stock/ETF's nearest prior announced dividend date

optvol_eod.name: optvol_eod
optvol_eod.description: Previous Day Options Volume is the total number of contracts bought and sold for the previous day, for a particular strike price

optvol.name: optvol
optvol.description: Options Volume is the total number of contracts bought and sold for that day, for a particular strike price

optvolcall_eod.name: optvolcall_eod
optvolcall_eod.description: Previous Day's Call Option Volume. Total number of call option contracts traded during the previous day

optvolcall.name: optvolcall
optvolcall.description: Call Options Volume is the total number of contracts bought and sold for that day, for a particular strike price

optvolput_eod.name: optvolput_eod
optvolput_eod.description: Previous Day's Put Option Volume. Total number of Put option contracts traded during the previous day

optvolput.name: optvolput
optvolput.description: Put Options Volume is the total number of contracts bought and sold for that day, for a particular strike price

openinterest_eod.name: openinterest_eod
openinterest_eod.description: Open Interest at Previous close. Open Interest refers to the total number of open contracts i.e. contracts which have been traded but not yet liquidated (liquidity indicator)

openinterest.name: openinterest
openinterest.description: Open Interest at Previous close. Open Interest refers to the total number of open contracts i.e. contracts which have been traded but not yet liquidated (liquidity indicator)

openinterestcall_eod.name: openinterestcall_eod
openinterestcall_eod.description: Call Open Interest at Previous close. Open Interest refers to the total number of open contracts i.e. contracts which have been traded but not yet liquidated (liquidity indicator)

openinterestput_eod.name: openinterestput_eod
openinterestput_eod.description: Put Open Interest at Previous close. Open Interest refers to the total number of open contracts i.e. contracts which have been traded but not yet liquidated (liquidity indicator)

stockvolume_eod.name: stockvolume_eod
stockvolume_eod.description: Previous Day's Stock Volume. Stock Volume is the actual number of stock shares traded on a particular day. SPX volume is composed as weighted volume from its components

stockvolume.name: stockvolume
stockvolume.description: Stock Volume is the actual number of stock shares traded on a particular day

avgoptvol1wk_eod.name: avgoptvol1wk_eod
avgoptvol1wk_eod.description: 1WK Avg Opt Volume is the average daily options volume (the total number of option contracts traded during the day) for the previous calendar week (only trading days are included). Updated around 7:30-8:00 PM EST, so the current average is for the previous day

avgoptoi1wk_eod.name: avgoptoi1wk_eod
avgoptoi1wk_eod.description: 1WK Avg Opt OI is the average daily options open interest (the total number of option contracts for a security that haven't been closed or delivered) for the previous calendar week (only trading days are included). Updated around 7:30-8:00 PM EST, so it is delayed one day from our reception

avgoptvol1mo_eod.name: avgoptvol1mo_eod
avgoptvol1mo_eod.description: 1MO Avg Opt Volume is the average daily options volume (the total number of traded options contracts traded during the day) for the last calendar month (only trading days are included), updated around 7:30-8:00 PM EST

avgoptoi1mo_eod.name: avgoptoi1mo_eod
avgoptoi1mo_eod.description: 1MO Avg Opt OI is the average daily options open interest (the total number of traded options contracts that haven't been closed or delivered) for the last calendar month (only trading days are included). Updated around 7:30-8:00 PM EST, so it is delayed one day from our reception

callputvolumeratio.name: callputvolumeratio
callputvolumeratio.description: Call/Put Volume Ratio. Ratio of total calls volume / total puts volume

callputvolumeratio_eod.name: callputvolumeratio_eod
callputvolumeratio_eod.description: Previous Day's Call/Put Ratio. Total calls volume / total puts volume for the previous day.

putcallvolumeratio.name: putcallvolumeratio
putcallvolumeratio.description: Put/Call Volume Ratio. Ratio of total puts volume / total calls volume

putcallvolumeratio_eod.name: putcallvolumeratio_eod
putcallvolumeratio_eod.description: Previous Day's Put/Call Ratio. Total puts volume / total calls volume for the previous day

ivx30_eod.description: Previous Closing IVX30. IVX is the composite measure of the stock's implied volatility calculated from an option's price using proprietary methodology. See IVolatility knowledge base for more details. IVX30 is calculated for the forward 30 calendar days

ivx30chg_eod.name: ivx30chg_eod
ivx30chg_eod.description: Previous Day's IVX30 Change. Derived by comparing the previous closing Implied Volatility Index (IVX30) against the day before yesterday's closing value. This value is the total change for the previous day

ivx30chgpercent_eod.name: ivx30chgpercent_eod
ivx30chgpercent_eod.description: Previous Day's IVX30 Change %. Derived by comparing the previous closing Implied Volatility Index (IVX30) against the day before yesterday's closing value, this difference is then expressed as a percent change. This value is the total change for the previous day

ivr30_eod.name: ivr30_eod
ivr30_eod.description: IV Rank for 30 calendar days (%).The ATM average implied volatility relative to the highest and lowest values over the past 1-year. IVR 30 = (Current IV - 1-year IV30 low)/(1-year IV30 high - 1-year IV30 low)*100%.
